 x12xpedu xnpuxes selectable-text copyable-text" style="min-height: 0px;"><span class="x1lliihq">What’s the AOR and ROE complete when can I send them off?
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="">Chris will be downloading Telegram onto his personal computer and he is going to upload all the notarized documents that I have on the 2 TB hard drive. The converter cord that I picked up did not do as I wanted to. It did not read the hard drive whenever I applied it to my phone.</span></span><span class=""><span class="x3nfvp2 xxymvpz xlshs6z xqtp20y xexx8yu x1uc92m x18d9i69 x181vq82 x12lo8hy x152skdk" aria-hidden="true"><span class="x1c4vz4f x2lah0s">5:23 pm</span></span></span></div></div><div class="x1n2onr6 x1n327nk x18mqm2i xhsvlbd x14z9mp xz62fqu x1wbi8v6"><div class="x1bvqhpb xx3o462 xuxw1ft x78zum5 x6s0dn4 x12lo8hy x152skdk" data-testid="msg-meta"><span class="x1rg5ohu x16dsc37" dir="auto"><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xt0psk2 x1fj9vlw xhslqc4 x1hx0egp x1pg5gke xjb2p0i xo1l8bm xl2ypbo x1ic7a3i" style="--x-fontSize: 12px; --x-lineHeight: 8.5313px;">5:23 pm</span></span></div></div></div></div><span class=""></span><div class="x10l6tqk xyc4j8s xceh6e4"></div></div></div><div class="x1c4vz4f xs83m0k xdl72j9 x1g77sc7 x78zum5 xozqiw3 x1oa3qoh x12fk4p8 xeuugli x2lwn1j x1nhvcw1 x1q0g3np x6s0dn4 xken49m xexx8yu x18d9i69 x135b78x x11lfxj5 x10l6tqk xwa60dl xfvs6mw xej21xi"><div class="x1c4vz4f xs83m0k xdl72j9 x1g77sc7 xeuugli x2lwn1j xozqiw3 x1oa3qoh x12fk4p8 xexx8yu x1im30kd x18d9i69 x1djpfga xcxita6"><div></div></div></div></div><div class="x78zum5 xbfrwjf x8k05lb xeq5yr9 x1n2onr6 xrr41r3 xqcrz7y" data-testid="addon-bubble-container"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div tabindex="-1" class="" role="row"><div tabindex="-1" class="x1n2onr6 xscbp6u" data-id="2AB2B2602F9EED64FA6C" data-testid="conv-msg-2AB2B2602F9EED64FA6C"><div class="x78zum5 xdt5ytf" data-virtualized="false"><div class=""><div class="x78zum5 xdt5ytf x1hx0egp x1wxbj4f xds8fti xh1vicy x1rzuvji x1cy8zhl focusable-list-item x1klvx2g xahtqtb"><span class=""></span><div data-testid="msg-container" class="xp43t2z x5j5mwf xptal55 xjodkme x1lzera4 x1c4vz4f