Chris will be downloading Telegram onto his personal computer and he is going to upload all the notarized documents that I have on the 2 TB hard drive. The converter cord that I picked up did not do as I wanted to. It did not read the hard drive whenever I applied it to my phone.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="x1n2onr6 x1mzt3pk x126k92a x6ikm8r x10wlt62"><span data-testid="selectable-text" dir="ltr" class="x1f6kntn xjb2p0i x8r4c90 xo1l8bm x1ic7a3i x12xpedu xnpuxes selectable-text copyable-text" style="min-height: 0px;"><span class="x1lliihq">Once the AOR and ROE have been fully reviewed for accuracy, properly executed, notarized, and all supporting documentation is assembled, they can be prepared for submission as part of the overall administrative package. Before sending anything, I would like to complete a final review to ensure there are no deficiencies or corrections needed that could create delays later in the process.
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="">It's good to hear that Chris will be downloading Telegram to his personal computer. Since the adapter was unable to read the 2 TB hard drive through your phone, uploading the files directly from the computer should be a much more reliable solution. Once the notarized documents are uploaded, I can inventory what has been completed, identify any missing items, and determine wh…</span></span> <div role="button" tabindex="0" data-testid="caption-read-more-button" class="xuxw1ft x1ypdohk x1rg5ohu xo1mcw5 x1xlr1w8 x1hl2dhg xt0b8zv xbvygy2 x17f7hit xp30eni xhmieyt read-more-button">Read more</div><span class=""><span class="x3nfvp2 xxymvpz xlshs6z xqtp20y xexx8yu x1uc92m x18d9i69 x181vq82 x12lo8hy x152skdk" aria-hidden="true"><span class="x1c4vz4f x2lah0s xn6xy2s"></span><span class="x1c4vz4f x2lah0s">5:27 pm</span></span></span></div></div><div class="x1n2onr6 x1n327nk x18mqm2i xhsvlbd x14z9mp xz62fqu x1wbi8v6"><div class="x1bvqhpb xx3o462 xuxw1ft x78zum5 x6s0dn4 x12lo8hy x152skdk" data-testid="msg-meta" role="button"><span class="x1rg5ohu x16dsc37" dir="auto"><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xt0psk2 x1fj9vlw xhslqc4 x1hx0egp x1pg5gke xjb2p0i xo1l8bm xl2ypbo x1ic7a3i" style="--x-fontSize: 12px; --x-lineHeight: 8.5313px;">5:27 pm</span></span><div class="xhslqc4 x1rg5ohu x7phf20"><span aria-hidden="false" aria-label=" Read " class="x1rv0e52"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" class="" fill="currentColor"><title>wds-ic-read</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M14.73 6.01a1 1 0 0 1 1.41-.15l.01.01a1 1 0 0 1 .15 1.41L7.6 18.01a1 1 0 0 1-.73.37h-.05c-.26 0-.52-.11-.71-.3l-4.03-4.09a.99.99 0 0 1 0-1.41.99.99 0 0 1 1.41 0l3.25 3.29 7.99-9.86Zm5.71.12a1 1 0 0 1 1.41-.15h-.01a1 1 0 0 1 .15 1.41l-8.41 10.45a1 1 0 0 1-.73.37h-.05a1 1 0 0 1-.71-.3l-1.36-1.26a.55.55 0 0 1-.02-.81l.56-.68c.21-.2.53-.21.75-.03l.71.58 7.71-9.58Z"></path></svg></span></div></div></div></div></div><span class=""></span><div class="x10